title: Michael Michaud Sunflower Wire Earring
description:
These sunflower earrings pay tribute to one of four of Vincent Van Gogh’s still-life paintings that feature the eye-catching yellow blooms in Paris during the late summer of 1887. These stunning earrings can be worn all year round with a casual t-shirt or your favorite dressy outfit.

Details:

• Cast in bronze with a hand-patina finish

• Accented with a 24k gold finish, 22k gold leaf, and amber stones

• Silver vermeil ear wires

• Dimensions:  5/8 " round

• Clean with soap and water utilizing a damp cloth

• Handmade in the USA
